Is GMWM Object

Is the object a gts, imu, lts, wvar, or gmwm object?

is.gts(x)

is.imu(x)

is.lts(x)

is.gmwm(x)

is.wvar(x)

is.ts.model(x)

Arguments

x
A gts, imu, lts object.

Value

A logical value that indicates whether the object is of that class (TRUE) or not (FALSE).

Details

Uses inherits over is for speed.
